The following is the JSON (Javascript Object Notation) syntax for indexing elements inside an
array. Replace the default index definition with the following.

```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": true|false,
    "fields": {
      "<array-field-name>": {
        "type": "<array-element-data-type>"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
